summary: This mod adds a medim sized vampire/assassin/evil character home near dawnstar.
descriptionHtml:
Its only a quick mock up i made for one of my own characters, a vampire lord who was listener of the DB decided to make a lair for him rather than some crummy bedroom as he\'s an eternal listener.

Its my firt ever mod intended for personal use just though i would put it up as a resource. 

If there is enough demand on the mod i wil update and add to it.

The armour seen if the \'Tribunal Robes\' Mod and awesome armour set check it out!

Thanks, 
OrionsAura
